With the USmart Home skill and our smart hardware, you can now interact with your light, plug, TV, air conditioner, curtain via Alexa.

Here is step by step guide:
1. Open our web app (https://h5.kiwik.cn) in mobile browser;
2. Sign up an account or just sign in if you’re already registered;
3. Setup your smart devices via our web app;
4. You may want to rename your devices in our web app so that Alexa will identify your devices;
5. In Alexa app, search and enable the skill “USmart Home”, then follow the wizard to link your account;
6. Now all setup is finished and devices are discovered by Alexa.
You can control your devices by voice, try talk to Alexa like these:
"Alexa, turn on bedroom light"
"Alexa, turn on TV"

Remind: You may need to re-discover devices after you make change to devices.

If you encountered any problems, please kindly contact us: support@kiwik.cn
